WEBVTT

00:00:59.720 --> 00:01:02.000
"Hey, why are you so short?"

00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.016
So I looked up and I said,

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:07.736
"What are you talking about?
Let's just play. We're happy.

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:09.120
I've been waiting for this."

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.096
And so we played,
and about a minute later,

00:01:12.120 --> 00:01:15.776
the girl next to him,
in a white shirt and a pink skirt,

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:17.536
stood up, put her hands on her hips,

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:20.600
and said, "Yeah,
why do you look so different?"

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:24.456
And I went, "What are you talking about?

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:27.840
I don't look different. I'm not short.
Again, let's just play."

00:01:28.520 --> 00:01:32.016
About this time, I looked
all around the circle I was in,